  }, "The Influence of Mothers and Women of God - Mother's Day Talk - 5.9.2021")), mdx("br", null), mdx("p", null, "Well, I knew coming into this, this was going to be a very daunting task. Mother's day is probably the most important day to prepare a good talk. And I ", mdx("em", {
