    parentName: "p"
  }, "twice"), " - another influence of my mom. On my mission there wasn't a single week that she failed to send me an email."), mdx("p", null, "I'm going to reread that scripture and this time I'm going to replace references of heavenly father with mom: I say unto you that if ye should serve your ", mdx("em", {
